name: Golden Core is a Star, and You Call This Cultivation?
summary:
My name is Qi Yuan, a transmigrator who became the senior brother of the Seven-Colored Peak.I have a game jade slip that can access the heavens.

My eyes can see hidden information.

[This is an ordinary blade of grass, but three days ago, True Lord Kumu and the Queen of Shang had a secret meeting here.] [Her name is Ruan Yixi, she appears to be your beautiful master, but she might actually be your wife.] 

[This is the Heavenly Dao of the world, the best spiritual item for Foundation Establishment.] 

[This is a planet without life, maybe you can refine it into your Golden Core.]

Thus, my path of cultivation started becoming strange.

“Heavenly Dao? Isn’t this the spiritual item for Foundation Establishment?”

“So many desolate planets, let’s refine them all into Golden Cores!”

Using the Heavenly Dao for Foundation Establishment, refining stars into Golden Cores.

My name is Qi Yuan, the origin of all things!

…

My name is Jiang Lingsu, I joined the Seven-Colored Peak with ulterior motives. My senior brother has a problem with his head.

He is irresponsible, dislikes cultivation, and is addicted to simulation games.

Senior brother said, “Games are cultivation, games can also create worlds.”

One day, an extra sun appeared in the sky.

I asked senior brother, what is that?

Senior brother said, “That’s my Golden Core!”
author: Running Crane
genres: Comedy, Adventure, Martial Arts, Drama, Fantasy, Slice of Life, Action, Harem, Tragedy, Xianxia, Xuanhuan, Mystery, Supernatural
